nodes.text: Unidentified clone trooper sergeant  (Decoy Squad Five)

A clone trooper sergeant led Decoy Squad Five, an eight-man clone trooper unit assigned to eliminate any Jedi who attempted to return to the Jedi Temple on Coruscant in the wake of Order 66. The sergeant was killed when two Jedi Masters, Obi-Wan Kenobi and Yoda, infiltrated the Jedi Temple.
